# Ignore everything by default
*

# --- Keep project sources & configs ---
!src/
!include/
!lib/
!docs/
!images/
!platformio.ini
!*.h
!*.c
!*.cpp
!*.md
!LICENSE


# --- Allow .pio folder but only final firmware files ---
!.pio/
!.pio/build/

# RP2040 (Pico, Pico W, Pico 2, Pico 2 W) - final UF2
!**/firmware.uf2

# ESP8266/ESP32 - final BIN
!**/firmware.bin

# --- Explicitly ignore all other build artifacts ---
*.elf
*.map
*.lst
*.bin
*.uf2
*.hex
*.d
*.o
*.a

# But keep only the "firmware" outputs we unignored above
!.pio/build/**/firmware.uf2
!.pio/build/**/firmware.bin
